{"tid":2170416,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"綠帽模擬器體驗被偷情滋味 ，Don't Cheat On Me 支援多人連線","createTime":"2020-08-23T09:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T20:02:53.000Z","uid":105678,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9f2fa65e6f45dd810ebd384e2fd5660b9e5db5","tid":2170416,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/ss_beb146fe50d35951f2b04049ef5f4b622ec2ecdb.600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fss_beb146fe50d35951f2b04049ef5f4b622ec2ecdb.600x338.jpg&h=052d4aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam 平台將會推出一款名為《Don&rsquo;t Cheat On Me》綠帽模擬器，玩家們可感受偷情與被偷情的滋味，更可多人連線遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n《Don&rsquo;t Cheat On Me》故事講述一對夫妻之間有第三者，這位鄰居勾引對面別人的妻子，展開一段偷情故事。遊戲中玩家可扮演妻子、丈夫還是第三者。如果你選擇戴綠帽，就要在屋中搜尋妻子偷情的證據，趁第三者進來偷情時捉個正著。相反如果做第三者的話，就要設法毀滅到家來訪的證據，甚至有時要匿藏起來，故事中會出現丈夫不可告人的秘密，如果掌握對方痛腳就可反客為主。如果選擇做妻子，同樣要銷毀任何出軌的證據，而且在丈夫回家時，要用盡方法引開他的注意力。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲規格中表明支援「多人」遊玩，但廠商未有解釋如何多人遊玩。《Don&rsquo;t Cheat On Me》預計在今年 12 月正式推出。"},{"pid":"8f93826fbd3440e269d9fbf702e8b2b65e53f430","tid":2170416,"uid":156936,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"外國間屋咁大就話難姐<br />\n整個香港mod  一眼睇晒 即刻gg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fec54eda240eec63970225220010b27ad919c9","tid":2170416,"uid":77355,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"台灣風化模擬器"},{"pid":"872924ff1166f54ed95037203cc7318900ec67da","tid":2170416,"uid":290083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T09:29:44.000Z","msg":"更可多人連線遊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e1734ddb962a31ccef2822dd922fd8426331f","tid